32:41.955 --> 32:44.355
which has to be portuguese
for "perpetual motion."

32:44.395 --> 32:46.315
It was fantastic.

32:46.315 --> 32:48.155
Where'd you wind up?

32:48.195 --> 32:51.155
Aha. You got milk all over
your whiskers, pussycat.

32:51.195 --> 32:53.555
Who was the lucky girl?
Where'd you meet her?

32:53.595 --> 32:54.995
I didn't meet anybody.

32:54.995 --> 32:56.435
Ok, ok.
We'll talk at breakfast.

32:56.435 --> 32:59.795
I want to know
all the details about her.

32:59.835 --> 33:03.155
You can start at the bottom
if you like.

33:06.035 --> 33:09.475
So did you kids have fun
at the wedding?

33:09.515 --> 33:12.955
Oh, yeah. Us kids had fun
at the wedding.

33:12.995 --> 33:13.875
Ow!

33:13.915 --> 33:14.875
Let me kiss it.

33:14.915 --> 33:15.795
Are you crazy?

33:15.835 --> 33:17.755
They're outside
having breakfast.

33:17.755 --> 33:21.595
Kiss me.

33:24.435 --> 33:25.395
Jennifer,
about last night-

33:25.435 --> 33:26.355
kiss me first.

33:26.355 --> 33:27.555
Kiss you?
I ought to spank you.

33:27.595 --> 33:28.755
Oh, please,
and bite me, too.

33:28.795 --> 33:31.115
Now stop that.

33:31.155 --> 33:32.795
Did you get
my sand flower?

33:32.835 --> 33:34.075
Oh, was that yours?
I did.

33:34.075 --> 33:35.275
It was lovely.
Thank you.

33:35.315 --> 33:36.275
You're lovely.

33:36.315 --> 33:37.155
No, I'm not.

33:37.195 --> 33:38.395
You're a fantastic lover.

33:38.435 --> 33:39.555
Don't talk
like that.

33:39.595 --> 33:41.475
Why? Will you tell
my father on me?

33:41.515 --> 33:43.915
There's nothing to tell.
Last night never happened.

33:43.955 --> 33:45.795
I know. I was there
when it didn't.

33:45.835 --> 33:48.475
No, I mean it.
It was just one wild moment.

33:48.515 --> 33:51.115
That's all it was.
You've got to forget it.

33:51.155 --> 33:52.555
We've both got to forget it.

33:52.595 --> 33:53.955
I was just
a one-night stand?

33:53.995 --> 33:57.355
No, no, no, no.
You're more than that.

33:57.395 --> 33:58.755
Am I?

33:58.795 --> 34:00.235
Jennifer, don't.

34:00.275 --> 34:02.395
What's the matter?

34:02.435 --> 34:04.195
You're too next to me.

34:04.235 --> 34:05.995
You want me to go?

34:05.995 --> 34:07.395
You'd better.

34:07.435 --> 34:11.715
One kiss,
and I will.

34:11.755 --> 34:14.635
All right.

34:14.675 --> 34:17.475
A little one.

34:27.635 --> 34:29.554
Good morning, daddy.

34:29.554 --> 34:31.955
What happened to my coffee
in bed this morning?

34:31.995 --> 34:33.355
I forgot.

34:33.395 --> 34:35.795
We're here one night,
and already I've lost you.

34:35.835 --> 34:39.155
Maybe you've
gained a son.

34:39.195 --> 34:40.554
What does that mean?

34:40.594 --> 34:42.034
Should I know
what that means?

34:42.074 --> 34:43.475
That's just Nicky.

34:43.514 --> 34:44.915
"Just Nicky" what?

34:44.955 --> 34:46.435
Being Nicky.

34:46.435 --> 34:50.755
What's on your face?

34:50.795 --> 34:55.034
Whipped cream.

34:55.074 --> 34:57.235
Tell me the truth,
Jennifer.

34:57.275 --> 34:59.355
Are you having fun so far?

34:59.395 --> 35:03.715
I want this to be the best
time we ever had together.

35:03.755 --> 35:04.635
I love you no matter

35:04.675 --> 35:07.075
what rotten things
your mother says about me.

35:07.115 --> 35:08.995
She doesn't say
anything bad about you

35:09.035 --> 35:10.875
yeah, but you can't
always believe her.

35:10.915 --> 35:14.075
Hey, not too many grapes.
They're hard to digest.

35:14.115 --> 35:15.515
Good morning, everyone.

35:15.555 --> 35:17.915
Sleep well,
uncle Matthew?

35:17.955 --> 35:20.315
Yes, I slept fine,
thank you.

35:20.355 --> 35:21.235
Hey, another egg.

35:21.275 --> 35:23.675
We really struck fertility
around here.

35:23.715 --> 35:25.795
Must be something
in the water.

35:25.835 --> 35:27.555
Nicky tells me
the wedding was fun.

35:27.595 --> 35:29.315
It seemed all right
the few minutes I-

35:29.355 --> 35:31.675
I was there.

35:31.715 --> 35:33.115
You meet any nice boys?

35:33.155 --> 35:35.355
I wasn't there
long enough.

35:35.395 --> 35:37.075
I asked Jennifer.

35:37.115 --> 35:38.595
Eh?

35:38.635 --> 35:40.035
Oh.

35:40.075 --> 35:41.875
One. One nice boy.

35:41.915 --> 35:47.715
Ah, terrific.

35:47.715 --> 35:50.075
What the hell's
the matter with you?

35:50.115 --> 35:52.435
I'm sorry. I'm just
a little jumpy.

35:52.475 --> 35:54.275
What are you jumpy about?

35:54.275 --> 35:55.675
I don't know.

35:55.675 --> 35:57.115
I didn't sleep
very well.

35:57.155 --> 35:59.075
You said
you slept fine.

35:59.115 --> 36:00.915
Then that must be it.

36:00.955 --> 36:02.875
You started smoking
again, too.

36:02.915 --> 36:07.675
Me? No.

36:16.115 --> 36:18.515
I think I'll make
a fresh watercress salad

36:18.555 --> 36:19.955
pick me out a couple
of nice bunches.

36:19.995 --> 36:20.915
No droopy ones

36:20.955 --> 36:21.835
right.

36:21.875 --> 36:23.315
You sure you won't
change your mind

36:23.355 --> 36:24.275
about after dinner

36:24.315 --> 36:25.675
I'm sure.

36:25.715 --> 36:28.115
Isabella's friend's just
been separated, too.

36:28.155 --> 36:29.995
You can't miss

36:30.035 --> 36:31.955
Victor, I am not
looking not to miss.

36:31.995 --> 36:33.395
You know what these are?

36:33.435 --> 36:34.315
Fruta de caja.

36:34.355 --> 36:35.795
Supposed to be
an aphrodisiac.

36:35.835 --> 36:36.995
It's all in the mind.

36:37.035 --> 36:38.195
Want to find out?

36:38.195 --> 36:39.595
No, thanks

36:39.635 --> 36:42.035
you're not seeing that little
lady from last night again?

36:42.035 --> 36:43.435
No, no, no

36:43.435 --> 36:45.355
I won't be seeing
Karen for a month.

36:45.395 --> 36:47.275
Just eat one
and put yourself on hold.

36:47.315 --> 36:48.235
Hello, hello.

36:48.275 --> 36:49.635
Hi.

36:49.675 --> 36:51.115
How nice. You are buying
groceries together.

36:51.155 --> 36:53.435
You are, how you say,
the queer couple?

36:53.475 --> 36:55.315
Odd couple, odd.

36:55.355 --> 36:58.235
Yes. May I present
senhor Hollis,

36:58.275 --> 36:59.555
senhor Lyons.

36:59.595 --> 37:00.475
Hello.

37:00.515 --> 37:01.435
Shopping for
the restaurant?

37:01.475 --> 37:03.875
No. Just a few things
for myself.

37:03.915 --> 37:06.715
Good day, my friends.

37:06.755 --> 37:11.835
I wonder if you
can freeze these.

37:17.195 --> 37:19.115
I love doing this.

37:19.115 --> 37:21.515
I haven't fixed dinner
for Jennifer in years.

37:21.555 --> 37:22.915
Hmm?

37:22.955 --> 37:25.355
Gonna put some meat
on her bones this trip

37:25.395 --> 37:27.275
I think she's too thin,
don't you?

37:27.315 --> 37:28.675
What?

37:28.715 --> 37:31.595
Don't you think
Jennifer's too skinny?

37:31.635 --> 37:33.955
She looks just fine to me.

37:33.995 --> 37:38.395
You think maybe that's
why Karen backed out,

37:38.435 --> 37:39.315
so you and Nicky

37:39.355 --> 37:40.795
could spend
some time together

37:40.835 --> 37:43.395
I don't think so.

37:43.435 --> 37:46.635
I don't know.

37:46.675 --> 37:49.795
Maybe, huh?

37:49.835 --> 37:54.115
I bet a son's easier.

37:54.155 --> 37:56.035
Do you really know what's
going on with Nicky?

37:56.075 --> 37:57.955
I mean, like, with boys.

37:57.955 --> 38:00.355
She did ask permission
to go on the pill.

38:00.395 --> 38:02.755
Oh, yeah?
What did you say?

38:02.795 --> 38:04.155
We said yes.

38:04.195 --> 38:07.075
Think of the possible
consequences otherwise.

38:07.115 --> 38:09.155
Not me

38:09.195 --> 38:11.155
what?

38:11.195 --> 38:14.355
I said no.

38:14.395 --> 38:15.795
No?

38:15.795 --> 38:18.195
Jennifer asked me
last summer.

38:18.235 --> 38:20.595
She asked you
about the pill?

38:20.635 --> 38:21.515
Right.

38:21.555 --> 38:23.435
And you said no?

38:23.475 --> 38:25.395
I told her
it's up to her

38:25.435 --> 38:27.315
whether she
takes it or not.

38:27.355 --> 38:29.795
Oh, I see.

38:29.795 --> 38:33.155
If she does, it's
without my blessing.

38:33.195 --> 38:35.555
All I care
is that she tell me.

38:35.595 --> 38:37.915
Tell you what?

38:37.955 --> 38:41.515
Well, we have a pact.

38:41.555 --> 38:42.435
Pact?

38:42.475 --> 38:44.355
What sort of pact?

38:44.395 --> 38:46.755
Well, if she and some boy
are at that point

38:46.795 --> 38:50.155
in their relationship where
they're gonna-you know-

38:50.195 --> 38:51.595
she's gonna tell me first.

38:51.635 --> 38:52.515
First?

38:52.555 --> 38:53.475
Well, before, really.

38:53.515 --> 38:55.915
How the hell
is she gonna do that?

38:55.915 --> 38:58.315
She'll give me a call.

38:58.355 --> 39:00.675
You're not serious

39:00.675 --> 39:02.355
you don't really think
she's gonna stop

39:02.395 --> 39:04.035
right in the middle
of whatever it is

39:04.075 --> 39:05.675
they're doing
and give you a call?

39:05.715 --> 39:06.875
Not in the middle.
Before.

39:06.915 --> 39:12.395
But suppose there's
no phone on the beach.

39:12.435 --> 39:13.915
What beach?

39:13.915 --> 39:15.315
Any beach.

39:15.355 --> 39:17.275
If, by chance,
it happened on a beach

39:17.315 --> 39:18.995
happens
on a beach

39:18.995 --> 39:22.835
and I don't say
that it did or will.

39:22.875 --> 39:24.075
Hey.

39:24.115 --> 39:25.195
What?

39:25.235 --> 39:27.115
We made a pact.

39:27.155 --> 39:34.435
I trust her
not to break it.

39:44.235 --> 39:45.675
What's all this?

39:45.715 --> 39:47.355
Surprised?

39:47.395 --> 39:48.675
Fantastic.

39:48.715 --> 39:49.955
So romantic.

39:49.995 --> 39:52.395
No, it's not.
We're just loving fathers.

39:52.435 --> 39:54.275
I love
loving fathers.

39:54.315 --> 39:55.755
Ah, good evening,
mademoiselle.

39:55.795 --> 39:56.675
Dinner is served.

39:56.715 --> 39:58.395
Oh, I don't
want any.

39:58.395 --> 40:00.035
It's chateaubriand

40:00.075 --> 40:01.995
no steak for me.
I'm a vegetarian.

40:01.995 --> 40:02.795
Since when?

40:02.835 --> 40:04.235
I am no longer
a carnivore.

40:04.275 --> 40:06.195
I don't eat anything
that's ever had parents.

40:06.235 --> 40:08.595
We have artichokes.
They're orphans.

40:08.635 --> 40:10.275
Where are you going?

40:10.315 --> 40:11.955
Out. I need
my sweater.

40:11.995 --> 40:12.915
With him?

40:12.955 --> 40:13.835
Yes.

40:13.875 --> 40:15.315
What's his name?

40:15.355 --> 40:16.235
Diego.

40:16.275 --> 40:17.235
You're not going
anywhere

40:17.275 --> 40:21.475
till I meet him.

40:21.475 --> 40:25.635
You, come here.

40:25.675 --> 40:28.555
Diego,
this is my father.

40:28.555 --> 40:29.515
Does he speak?

40:29.555 --> 40:30.435
He's a drummer.

40:30.475 --> 40:32.875
Can he beat out hello
on the table?

40:32.875 --> 40:34.795
Daddy,
he's an artist.

40:34.835 --> 40:36.675
He's also
a carnivore.

40:36.715 --> 40:42.395
Come on.

40:42.435 --> 40:48.115
Good. I have you both
to myself.

40:52.595 --> 40:54.515
Whisper low

40:54.555 --> 40:56.435
how you feel

40:56.435 --> 41:00.275
let your eyes
speak your mind

41:00.315 --> 41:02.675
search your heart

41:02.715 --> 41:04.075
am I right?

41:04.115 --> 41:07.955
Is it love
that you find?

41:08.035 --> 41:11.875
Did you know
it could be

41:11.915 --> 41:17.435
a new world
in the making

41:17.435 --> 41:22.355
tonight alone with me?

41:22.395 --> 41:27.195
I could shout
how I feel

41:27.235 --> 41:31.355
but the truth
still must hide

41:31.395 --> 41:33.275
so for now...?

41:33.315 --> 41:35.635
To, uh...

41:35.675 --> 41:38.835
the 2 people
closest to my heart.

41:38.875 --> 41:41.155
2 people who make
me feel that, uh...

41:41.195 --> 41:43.435
well, I must be
worth something,

41:43.475 --> 41:45.635
because if
they love me,

41:45.675 --> 41:46.955
then i, uh

41:46.995 --> 41:48.395
can't be as
bad as someone

41:48.435 --> 41:50.835
who's the mother of
one of those 2 people

41:50.875 --> 41:52.235
thinks I am.

41:52.275 --> 41:54.515
Worthy or not,

41:54.555 --> 41:56.035
I love you both.

41:56.075 --> 41:57.555
I gotta run.

41:57.555 --> 41:58.275
Wait.

41:58.315 --> 41:59.635
I'm late already.

41:59.635 --> 42:01.675
You're not gonna leave
Jennifer here alone, are you?

42:01.715 --> 42:03.075
Why?

42:03.115 --> 42:04.075
You coming with me

42:04.075 --> 42:04.995
no.

42:05.035 --> 42:06.955
Well, then you'll
baby-sit.

42:06.955 --> 42:07.875
If she misbehaves,

42:07.915 --> 42:11.235
I want you to put her
over your knee, ok?

42:11.275 --> 42:12.195
Good night, sweetheart

42:12.195 --> 42:13.635
good night, daddy.
Have fun.

42:13.675 --> 42:17.475
Ok. You, too.

42:20.475 --> 42:22.875
There's nothing
to smile about.

42:22.875 --> 42:24.275
This will give us a chance

42:24.315 --> 42:28.595
to straighten this thing
between us out
once and for all.

42:28.635 --> 42:31.475
Jennifer.

42:31.475 --> 42:35.315
Are you listening to me?

42:41.355 --> 42:43.715
What?

42:43.755 --> 42:45.675
G
I was just
rememberin

42:45.715 --> 42:48.355
the first time
I kissed you.

42:48.355 --> 42:50.915
It was at your
christening.

42:50.955 --> 42:53.355
Your mother was
powdering your bottom,

42:53.395 --> 42:54.755
d
and I said I wante

42:54.795 --> 42:57.915
to be the first man
to kiss it.

42:57.955 --> 43:00.995
And I leaned over,
and I did.

43:01.035 --> 43:04.395
How dare you drive
a tiny baby wild with desire.

43:04.435 --> 43:05.795
Oops!

43:05.835 --> 43:07.275
They happen to use these
for birth control.

43:07.315 --> 43:13.955
Which one of us
wears it?

43:13.995 --> 43:20.675
I must be doing
something right

43:27.115 --> 43:29.995
you should wear
your hair like this.

43:30.035 --> 43:30.915
What time is it?

43:30.955 --> 43:34.315
About 1:00.
I like it like this.

43:34.355 --> 43:36.235
It makes you look older.

43:36.275 --> 43:37.915
It's almost 3:00.

43:37.955 --> 43:39.555
Pretend it's 1:00.

43:39.595 --> 43:41.035
We've done too much
pretending lately.

43:41.035 --> 43:42.715
You have to go

43:42.755 --> 43:44.355
let me stay.

43:44.395 --> 43:46.275
We don't have
to make love again.

43:46.315 --> 43:48.235
I promise not to
get you excited.

43:48.275 --> 43:50.115
I'll just bite
your neck a little.

43:50.155 --> 43:51.355
Jennifer.

43:51.395 --> 43:52.475
Meanie.

43:52.515 --> 43:55.395
I've never spent
the whole night

43:55.435 --> 43:57.275
Nicky must be
home by now.

43:57.315 --> 44:00.195
You always have to
worry about something.

44:00.235 --> 44:03.155
Your father told me
about your pact.

44:03.195 --> 44:06.035
Which pact?
My father just loves pacts.

44:06.035 --> 44:08.835
He said you'd tell him
that if you and a boy

44:08.875 --> 44:10.475
ever, um...

44:10.515 --> 44:12.075
"ever, um?"

44:12.075 --> 44:14.955
Do you think I'd "um"
with a boy?

44:14.995 --> 44:17.795
Do you think
I'm that kind of girl?

44:17.835 --> 44:20.235
I just promised daddy
to make him feel better.

44:20.275 --> 44:23.115
I never meant
to really tell him.

44:23.155 --> 44:24.035
You've got us
both wrapped

44:24.075 --> 44:26.475
round your little
finger, haven't you?

44:26.515 --> 44:27.875
I love you.

44:27.915 --> 44:30.795
I can't think of a time
when I ever didn't.

44:30.835 --> 44:33.635
Jennifer, it's late.

44:33.675 --> 44:36.555
I love it when
your glasses steam up.

44:36.595 --> 44:38.915
Only when I'm with you

44:38.955 --> 44:41.355
you know what I used to
pretend when I was little?

44:41.395 --> 44:43.515
I'm afraid to guess.

44:43.555 --> 44:45.675
That we were married.

44:45.675 --> 44:46.875
You and me

44:46.915 --> 44:48.675
when I was 10.

44:48.715 --> 44:50.435
And I was only 90.

44:50.435 --> 44:53.795
It would be lovely,
being married.

44:53.835 --> 44:55.715
Jennifer,
married people

44:55.715 --> 44:58.115
do not go around
getting married.

44:58.155 --> 45:01.475
Then maybe
just a honeymoon.

45:01.515 --> 45:04.755
Off you go

45:04.795 --> 45:07.955
off to bed

45:07.995 --> 45:09.435
it took whatever
strength I had

45:09.475 --> 45:11.315
to send her away.

45:11.355 --> 45:12.795
That's not
altogether true.

45:12.835 --> 45:14.195
If I really had
any strength,

45:14.235 --> 45:16.915
she never would've
been there at all.

45:16.955 --> 45:19.755
Jennifer.

45:19.795 --> 45:20.995
You all right?

45:21.035 --> 45:22.155
I'm fine, daddy.

45:22.195 --> 45:23.635
How come you're up
so late?

45:23.675 --> 45:26.035
How come you are?

45:26.075 --> 45:27.435
Touchi.

45:27.475 --> 45:28.915
Good night,
sweetheart

45:28.955 --> 45:30.835
good night, daddy.

45:30.875 --> 45:33.475
P- u!

45:33.515 --> 45:36.115
Cigar!

45:41.755 --> 45:43.275
Nicky,

45:43.315 --> 45:45.995
do you hate me?

45:46.035 --> 45:49.795
No

45:49.835 --> 45:53.515
him.

45:53.555 --> 45:55.555
Does he tell you
he loves you?

45:55.595 --> 45:58.035
No.

45:58.075 --> 46:01.915
You'll get used to it.

46:09.395 --> 46:11.595
If you want a man
to love you,

46:11.635 --> 46:13.755
you must light
many, many candles

46:13.795 --> 46:16.275
and give gifts
to the goddess iamanja.

46:16.315 --> 46:18.155
The goddess iamanja?

46:18.195 --> 46:20.115
Throw flowers into the sea.

46:20.155 --> 46:21.035
White ones.

46:21.075 --> 46:21.995
If they come back,

46:22.035 --> 46:23.915
it means she has
rejected them.

46:23.955 --> 46:27.795
If not, she has listened
to your prayer.

46:27.995 --> 46:28.955
I'll do it.

46:28.995 --> 46:29.875
And here...

46:29.915 --> 46:35.275
have him
wear this always.

47:02.315 --> 47:03.355
You love me!

47:03.395 --> 47:04.715
The flowers
didn't come back.

47:04.755 --> 47:05.635
You love me.

47:05.675 --> 47:07.355
I want to tell
the whole world!

47:07.395 --> 47:10.275
I'm so happy.
The flowers didn't come back.

47:10.315 --> 47:11.195
You love me!

47:11.235 --> 47:15.875
You love me!
You love me!

47:15.915 --> 47:20.555
Jennifer, for god's sake.

47:20.595 --> 47:22.915
Here.

47:22.955 --> 47:23.875
