01:01:45.915 --> 01:01:48.755
Victor, Victor,
you can't.

01:01:48.795 --> 01:01:51.115
This isn't for me.

01:01:51.155 --> 01:01:53.075
What do you think,
I'm crazy?

01:01:53.115 --> 01:01:54.955
This is for him.

01:01:54.995 --> 01:01:58.115
I'm gonna find him,
and whoever he is,

01:01:58.155 --> 01:02:01.235
he's gonna get this
right up the doodah.

01:02:01.275 --> 01:02:05.715
Ciao.

01:02:05.755 --> 01:02:08.595
Nicky? Nicky?

01:02:08.635 --> 01:02:11.795
Where have you been
tonight? Last night?

01:02:11.795 --> 01:02:13.475
What do you care?

01:02:13.515 --> 01:02:15.115
I'm your father.

01:02:15.155 --> 01:02:16.675
Do I ask where you go?

01:02:16.715 --> 01:02:17.995
I have been here.

01:02:17.995 --> 01:02:20.715
Sure. This is
where the action is.

01:02:20.715 --> 01:02:23.355
I've played dumb
so often with you,

01:02:23.395 --> 01:02:27.075
I know when you're
playing dumb with me.

01:02:27.115 --> 01:02:30.955
I hope I'm as smart as you are
when I get to be your age.

01:02:30.995 --> 01:02:34.795
You always said that honesty
should never be painful.

01:02:34.835 --> 01:02:37.755
I was wrong.

01:02:37.755 --> 01:02:39.315
She's in love, you know.

01:02:39.355 --> 01:02:40.715
She thinks so.

01:02:40.755 --> 01:02:43.115
If you think so,
you are.

01:02:43.155 --> 01:02:45.075
The first is
always the hardest.

01:02:45.075 --> 01:02:46.515
You're not the first.

01:02:46.515 --> 01:02:48.395
Well, I know.

01:02:48.435 --> 01:02:50.875
They're all hard in a way.

01:02:50.915 --> 01:02:55.275
She'll get over you.
Just be yourself.

01:02:55.315 --> 01:02:59.155
I had to admit Jennifer
had gotten under my skin.

01:02:59.195 --> 01:03:01.515
I had no one
to turn to for advice.

01:03:01.555 --> 01:03:07.515
What I needed was
objective professional help.

01:03:12.315 --> 01:03:14.755
The more trouble
in heart and mind,

01:03:14.795 --> 01:03:18.635
the more candles you must burn
for the help of the gods.

01:03:18.675 --> 01:03:20.075
How young is the girl?

01:03:20.115 --> 01:03:21.515
Uh, she's quite young.

01:03:21.555 --> 01:03:23.675
Half your age?

01:03:23.715 --> 01:03:25.715
Less than half

01:03:25.755 --> 01:03:29.155
how many do I take

01:03:29.195 --> 01:03:32.515
take the whole box.

01:03:32.555 --> 01:03:35.875
A- ha!

01:03:44.915 --> 01:03:46.155
Matthew!
What?

01:03:46.195 --> 01:03:49.475
In here.

01:03:49.515 --> 01:03:52.875
Come in here!

01:03:52.915 --> 01:03:56.715
What's wrong?

01:03:56.755 --> 01:04:00.555
Close the door.

01:04:00.555 --> 01:04:02.715
What?

01:04:02.755 --> 01:04:05.115
Quiet. Wait.

01:04:05.155 --> 01:04:07.355
Shit!
What's going on?

01:04:07.395 --> 01:04:11.195
Jennifer's diary.

01:04:11.195 --> 01:04:12.115
Her diary?

01:04:12.155 --> 01:04:18.355
That's not all.
Iook at this.

01:04:18.355 --> 01:04:20.275
You can't look at that.
He took pictures of her.

01:04:20.315 --> 01:04:21.715
Oh, I'm sure
he wouldn't.

01:04:21.755 --> 01:04:23.155
He wouldn't, huh?

01:04:23.155 --> 01:04:28.075
He forced himself on her
at the beach, didn't he?

01:04:28.075 --> 01:04:29.275
Victor!

01:04:29.315 --> 01:04:30.435
What?

01:04:30.475 --> 01:04:32.835
You can't read that.
That is someone's

01:04:32.875 --> 01:04:34.755
private
personal property.

01:04:34.755 --> 01:04:40.515
Are you nuts?
Whose side are you on?

01:04:40.555 --> 01:04:42.395
Listen to this.

01:04:42.435 --> 01:04:44.315
"Last night
it finally happened.

01:04:44.355 --> 01:04:48.195
"We lay in the sand together,
my body next to his.

01:04:48.235 --> 01:04:50.595
"My legs, his legs,
each of us the other."

01:04:50.635 --> 01:04:51.795
Disgusting.

01:04:51.835 --> 01:04:53.875
She said that?

01:04:53.875 --> 01:04:55.835
I said that.

01:04:55.875 --> 01:04:57.275
It goes on and on.

01:04:57.315 --> 01:05:03.075
Come on, Jennifer,
what's his name?

01:05:03.115 --> 01:05:03.995
A- ha!

01:05:04.035 --> 01:05:05.515
Victor, I can explain.

01:05:05.555 --> 01:05:07.435
"He's all
I ever dreamed of.

01:05:07.475 --> 01:05:11.795
"He's a much better
lover than moose."

01:05:11.835 --> 01:05:14.155
Moose?

01:05:14.195 --> 01:05:15.595
Who the hell
is moose?

01:05:15.635 --> 01:05:17.035
Must be some kid
at school.

01:05:17.075 --> 01:05:18.515
She never told me
about him, either.

01:05:18.555 --> 01:05:20.435
How can you send her
to a school

01:05:20.475 --> 01:05:22.355
where the guys
are called "moose"

01:05:22.355 --> 01:05:23.315
explain what?

01:05:23.315 --> 01:05:24.235
What?

01:05:24.275 --> 01:05:25.795
You said you could
explain something.

01:05:25.835 --> 01:05:28.155
I can. Yes.

01:05:28.195 --> 01:05:31.555
This-this.
I can explain this

01:05:31.595 --> 01:05:33.955
it's youth.
That's all

01:05:33.995 --> 01:05:35.355
kids exaggerate.

01:05:35.395 --> 01:05:38.275
They make things up.
They make people up.

01:05:38.275 --> 01:05:40.155
Oh, yeah?

01:05:40.195 --> 01:05:42.915
Did she make this up?

01:05:42.955 --> 01:05:45.315
"I go to sleep with
his smile on my lips.

01:05:45.355 --> 01:05:48.715
"I love his sweet mouth.
His funny little teeth.

01:05:48.755 --> 01:05:51.275
"I love looking
deep into his soul

01:05:51.315 --> 01:05:54.275
"through his
lovely blue eyes,

01:05:54.315 --> 01:05:57.235
"eyes that seem
to see the real me

01:05:57.275 --> 01:05:59.675
"for the very first time."

01:05:59.715 --> 01:06:02.035
Why are you wearing those?

01:06:02.075 --> 01:06:03.275
I'm getting a sty.

01:06:03.275 --> 01:06:04.435
Just like that?

01:06:04.475 --> 01:06:07.795
How else?

01:06:12.115 --> 01:06:13.995
I don't believe it.

01:06:14.035 --> 01:06:15.475
She doesn't say
who he is anywhere.

01:06:15.515 --> 01:06:17.355
Nowhere?

01:06:17.395 --> 01:06:19.115
The hell with it.

01:06:19.155 --> 01:06:20.835
We got enough clues.

01:06:20.875 --> 01:06:21.835
Come on.

01:06:21.835 --> 01:06:22.715
Where?

01:06:22.755 --> 01:06:25.155
You and I are gonna
find that bastard.

01:06:25.195 --> 01:06:28.755
Wings to the sky

01:06:28.795 --> 01:06:31.555
floats
easy and free there?

01:06:31.595 --> 01:06:33.515
Try to think. Didn't
she tell you anything?

01:06:33.555 --> 01:06:34.915
You're her best friend.

01:06:34.955 --> 01:06:36.395
Sometimes even
best friends

01:06:36.395 --> 01:06:37.795
keep secrets
from each other.

01:06:37.835 --> 01:06:40.235
A nickname, a pet name.
Where he lives.

01:06:40.235 --> 01:06:41.155
Who can remember

01:06:41.155 --> 01:06:43.075
everyone she
goes out with?

01:06:43.115 --> 01:06:44.515
There's more
than one?

01:06:44.515 --> 01:06:47.315
Well, there's the dancer
at the club we were at.

01:06:47.355 --> 01:06:48.235
The singer, too.

01:06:48.275 --> 01:06:49.715
She's seeing
all of them?

01:06:49.755 --> 01:06:51.115
You know how it is, dad.

01:06:51.155 --> 01:06:52.555
When you're hot,
you're hot.

01:06:52.595 --> 01:06:54.995
Any of these guys
own a polaroid?

01:06:55.035 --> 01:06:56.395
What?

01:06:56.435 --> 01:06:59.915
Never mind.
Let's go.

01:06:59.955 --> 01:07:03.395
Be careful, Nicky.

01:07:03.435 --> 01:07:06.235
You're not really gonna
go up on that, are you

01:07:06.275 --> 01:07:09.075
I like to live dangerously.
Runs in the family.

01:07:09.115 --> 01:07:13.835
Days of your life

01:07:13.875 --> 01:07:16.995
these wings to the sky?

01:07:17.035 --> 01:07:19.915
I really appreciate
you not saying anything.

01:07:19.955 --> 01:07:22.315
My father's had
a lot of experience,

01:07:22.355 --> 01:07:24.235
but he'd never
understand this.

01:07:24.275 --> 01:07:25.435
I wish he knew, though.

01:07:25.475 --> 01:07:27.035
Why don't you tell him

01:07:27.035 --> 01:07:28.515
I want your dad to.

01:07:28.555 --> 01:07:29.995
He won't.
He's a coward.

01:07:30.035 --> 01:07:31.195
Mine's blind.

01:07:31.235 --> 01:07:32.515
I'll trade you

01:07:32.555 --> 01:07:33.795
I sort of have.

01:07:33.835 --> 01:07:35.715
Who'd you send him
to look for?

01:07:35.755 --> 01:07:38.155
Just a couple of guys
to throw them off the track.

01:07:38.155 --> 01:07:40.035
That's hysterical.
Who?

01:07:40.075 --> 01:07:41.995
Like the singer
at the club.

01:07:41.995 --> 01:07:43.395
He's gross

01:07:43.435 --> 01:07:45.315
that's why I picked him.

01:07:45.315 --> 01:07:48.395
You think your dad'll
get jealous?

01:07:48.435 --> 01:07:51.475
It's the least
I could do for him.

01:07:55.395 --> 01:07:57.715
Come up and dance!
Somebody! Anybody!

01:07:57.755 --> 01:08:02.515
Don't be shy!
Come up and dance!

01:08:11.595 --> 01:08:13.515
Uh, no. No. No.

01:08:13.515 --> 01:08:18.314
Not me.
I'm with my friend.

01:08:18.354 --> 01:08:20.234
No, I-I can't dance.

01:08:20.274 --> 01:08:23.075
I can't!

01:08:23.115 --> 01:08:26.475
I can't. I-I don't
know how to dance.

01:08:26.515 --> 01:08:29.795
Hi, uncle Matthew.

01:08:29.835 --> 01:08:31.995
It won't work,
you know.

01:08:32.035 --> 01:08:34.115
Trying to make
me jealous.

01:08:34.154 --> 01:08:36.154
You think you're
playing with a kid.

01:08:36.194 --> 01:08:38.995
You think you are.

01:08:39.035 --> 01:08:44.314
Please, I'm getting
over a bereavement

01:08:44.354 --> 01:08:46.234
your father
is out of his mind

01:08:46.274 --> 01:08:47.154
what else is new?

01:08:47.194 --> 01:08:48.635
And I'm not
much better.

01:08:48.675 --> 01:08:50.035
Really?

01:08:50.075 --> 01:08:51.955
I need time to think
things over.

01:08:51.995 --> 01:08:56.795
You don't have much time
at your age, do you?

01:08:59.675 --> 01:09:01.475
Did you really go out
with this android?

01:09:01.515 --> 01:09:03.035
I think he likes
you better.

01:09:03.035 --> 01:09:06.835
See you later.

01:09:13.835 --> 01:09:16.234
Well, what do you think?
Is he the guy?

01:09:16.274 --> 01:09:17.475
I don't know.

01:09:17.515 --> 01:09:18.635
You don't know?

01:09:18.635 --> 01:09:22.475
You want one more
dance with him?

01:09:26.715 --> 01:09:28.635
That guy's singing
right to her.

01:09:28.675 --> 01:09:30.035
It doesn't
mean anything.

01:09:30.075 --> 01:09:34.875
What are the words?
What's he singing?

01:09:38.675 --> 01:09:40.595
He says...

01:09:40.595 --> 01:09:42.515
"his love is the sea

01:09:42.515 --> 01:09:44.915
"that goes on
forever more."

01:09:44.955 --> 01:09:46.314
Yeah?

01:09:46.354 --> 01:09:48.274
"He lives
to return to her

01:09:48.314 --> 01:09:50.194
"again and again..."

01:09:50.234 --> 01:09:52.075
yeah?

01:09:52.115 --> 01:09:54.475
"And-and beat
against her shore.

01:09:54.515 --> 01:09:56.435
I'll give him
"beat against her shore."

01:09:56.475 --> 01:09:57.355
Victor

01:09:57.395 --> 01:09:59.715
Victor, don't!

01:09:59.715 --> 01:10:01.995
Daddy!

01:10:02.035 --> 01:10:04.275
No!

01:10:04.315 --> 01:10:07.995
Victor, stop it!

01:10:08.035 --> 01:10:11.675
Victor, don't!

01:10:14.755 --> 01:10:16.675
Victor, stop!

01:10:16.715 --> 01:10:18.995
Ohh!

01:10:19.035 --> 01:10:21.275
Victor!

01:10:24.635 --> 01:10:27.395
He's got brown eyes.

01:10:27.435 --> 01:10:29.315
Welcome, my friends.

01:10:29.315 --> 01:10:31.115
It's all yours-

01:10:31.155 --> 01:10:34.515
the night, the sky,
my city, my restaurant

01:10:34.555 --> 01:10:38.795
claudio, champagne

01:10:38.835 --> 01:10:40.755
this is not a night
to celebrate.

01:10:40.795 --> 01:10:42.675
You did not
find him?

01:10:42.675 --> 01:10:44.555
Not yet...

01:10:44.595 --> 01:10:46.275
but he can't
hide forever.

01:10:46.275 --> 01:10:47.915
Give it a rest, Victor.

01:10:47.955 --> 01:10:50.795
You can make yourself
sick over this.

01:10:50.835 --> 01:10:53.475
Gold.
The man is gold.

01:10:53.515 --> 01:10:56.035
As a friend
should be.

01:10:56.075 --> 01:10:58.955
Now we look
at the menu, yes?

01:10:58.995 --> 01:11:01.835
The stomach
also has a heart.

01:11:01.875 --> 01:11:05.155
Daddy?

01:11:05.195 --> 01:11:06.595
I've gotta
talk to you.

01:11:06.635 --> 01:11:08.555
Of course, sweetheart.
You want to be alone?

01:11:08.595 --> 01:11:13.995
This is fine.

01:11:14.035 --> 01:11:17.875
I love you, daddy,
very much.

01:11:17.955 --> 01:11:21.795
I can't let you go around
beating people up...

01:11:21.835 --> 01:11:27.555
getting hurt yourself...

01:11:27.595 --> 01:11:29.915
what happened...

01:11:29.955 --> 01:11:32.115
happened out of tenderness

01:11:32.115 --> 01:11:33.675
out of beautiful feelings.

01:11:33.715 --> 01:11:35.235
Don't think of it as ugly.

01:11:35.235 --> 01:11:37.595
I don't want to.

01:11:37.595 --> 01:11:39.395
Just tell me who it is,
sweetheart.

01:11:39.435 --> 01:11:44.715
Just tell me so we can
get this all behind us.

01:11:52.395 --> 01:11:53.795
You!

01:11:53.835 --> 01:11:57.635
Eu? Ela louca!

01:11:57.675 --> 01:11:59.955
I'll give you
louca!
Come here!

01:11:59.995 --> 01:12:00.915
Why didn't you tell him?

01:12:00.955 --> 01:12:02.355
You wanted me to.

01:12:02.395 --> 01:12:03.755
Yes.

01:12:03.795 --> 01:12:05.195
Then you'll tell him.

01:12:05.235 --> 01:12:09.555
You'll speak
for both of us.

01:12:13.955 --> 01:12:15.395
It could not be me.

01:12:15.435 --> 01:12:16.315
No, huh?

01:12:16.355 --> 01:12:17.755
I am impotent.

01:12:17.795 --> 01:12:19.715
I've seen you in the market
with young women.

01:12:19.755 --> 01:12:21.595
Shopping is no problem.

01:12:21.635 --> 01:12:23.075
Victor, does he
look 43 to you

01:12:23.115 --> 01:12:24.235
I am 57!

01:12:24.275 --> 01:12:26.035
Horseshit!

01:12:26.075 --> 01:12:27.755
All right. 61.

01:12:27.755 --> 01:12:29.675
He's too old.
He's not married.

01:12:29.715 --> 01:12:31.595
He's not anything
that diary said.

01:12:31.635 --> 01:12:33.995
You said kids
invent things.

01:12:34.035 --> 01:12:35.875
And you saw her.

01:12:35.915 --> 01:12:38.315
She stared
right at him.

01:12:38.355 --> 01:12:39.235
It's him!

01:12:39.275 --> 01:12:40.915
It's not anyone
we've seen!

01:12:40.955 --> 01:12:44.275
How do you know?

01:12:44.315 --> 01:12:47.635
Because it's me.

01:12:54.635 --> 01:12:57.355
You.

01:12:57.395 --> 01:13:00.075
Me.

01:13:00.075 --> 01:13:05.355
Say something,
Victor.

01:13:05.395 --> 01:13:09.835
Hit me.

01:13:09.875 --> 01:13:14.235
Hit him.

01:13:14.275 --> 01:13:18.515
Not hitting me feels
worse than if you did.

01:13:18.555 --> 01:13:23.115
How'd it happen?

01:13:23.155 --> 01:13:27.675
It was my fault.

01:13:27.715 --> 01:13:29.635
I take full
responsibility.

01:13:29.675 --> 01:13:32.195
That's big of you.

01:13:32.235 --> 01:13:34.155
It was the night
of the wedding.

01:13:34.155 --> 01:13:36.795
Ah, romance
was in the air.

01:13:36.835 --> 01:13:39.395
Birds, music,
dancing, drums.

01:13:39.435 --> 01:13:41.595
Everything at once.

01:13:41.635 --> 01:13:43.675
Blame it on Rio, eh?

01:13:43.715 --> 01:13:46.595
I wasn't thinking
what I was doing.

01:13:46.635 --> 01:13:48.115
You understand.

01:13:48.155 --> 01:13:50.915
It's only when a man is not
thinking of what he's doing

01:13:50.955 --> 01:13:53.715
that you can be sure he's
doing what he's thinking.

01:13:53.755 --> 01:13:54.635
Thanks.

01:13:54.675 --> 01:13:56.075
You were by my side

01:13:56.115 --> 01:13:58.835
the whole time we were
looking for him.

01:13:58.875 --> 01:14:02.995
What a horse's ass you
must have thought I was.

01:14:03.035 --> 01:14:04.395
I didn't have
the courage.

01:14:04.435 --> 01:14:09.235
Who asked you
for the courage now?

01:14:09.275 --> 01:14:12.115
Why'd you have
to tell me?

01:14:12.155 --> 01:14:14.035
In spite of it all,

01:14:14.075 --> 01:14:15.915
I'm your friend.

01:14:15.955 --> 01:14:16.875
If you were
really my friend,

01:14:16.915 --> 01:14:19.795
you would've kept quiet
about what you did.

01:14:19.835 --> 01:14:22.195
Which you never
would've done

01:14:22.235 --> 01:14:24.595
if you were
really my friend.

01:14:24.635 --> 01:14:26.515
Hit me.

01:14:26.555 --> 01:14:28.395
Please.

01:14:28.435 --> 01:14:30.235
Will you really
feel worse if I don't?

01:14:30.275 --> 01:14:32.115
Terrible.

01:14:32.155 --> 01:14:39.355
Good night, Matthew.

01:14:40.595 --> 01:14:42.115
Wrong is the urge

01:14:42.115 --> 01:14:44.035
that I feel to be simple

01:14:44.035 --> 01:14:46.275
when the light
falls just right

01:14:46.275 --> 01:14:48.475
and her eyes
are inviting me

01:14:48.515 --> 01:14:49.875
and who in the world

01:14:49.915 --> 01:14:56.035
is immune
to the sensual moon

01:14:56.075 --> 01:14:57.435
chills up my spine

01:14:57.475 --> 01:14:59.395
tell me
I'm just the victim

01:14:59.435 --> 01:15:01.275
without hope to resist

01:15:01.315 --> 01:15:03.715
it's a fever
that tears me down

01:15:03.755 --> 01:15:06.555
and if by some chance

01:15:06.595 --> 01:15:08.995
they should happen
to stumble on a cure

01:15:09.035 --> 01:15:11.915
don't tell me

01:15:11.955 --> 01:15:15.315
once temptation gets

01:15:15.355 --> 01:15:19.395
the best of me

01:15:19.435 --> 01:15:24.435
will these restless
feelings stir

01:15:24.475 --> 01:15:27.155
there's trouble

01:15:27.195 --> 01:15:35.555
once temptation
gets the best of me

01:15:35.595 --> 01:15:43.195
then I'm helpless
next to her

01:15:43.235 --> 01:15:47.075
chills up my spine tell me
I'm just the victim...?

01:15:47.075 --> 01:15:49.235
Psst!

01:15:49.275 --> 01:15:51.355
Matthew!

01:15:51.395 --> 01:15:52.315
