even more impossible.

01:16:47.475 --> 01:16:50.355
Stop hiding behind words
like "relationship."

01:16:50.395 --> 01:16:52.715
We're in love. You said.

01:16:52.755 --> 01:16:55.155
I was hoping, in my
usual dumb fashion

01:16:55.195 --> 01:16:56.555
