01:17:49.875 --> 01:17:52.875
That's all that matters.

01:18:09.195 --> 01:18:11.115
I just think you ought
to come right away.

01:18:11.155 --> 01:18:13.035
Are you all right?

01:18:13.075 --> 01:18:14.435
Nicole?

01:18:14.475 --> 01:18:16.395
Dad needs you.
He's in real trouble.

01:18:16.435 --> 01:18:18.275
What's happened?
Is he hurt?

01:18:18.315 --> 01:18:22.915
He's going to be, mom,
and not just him.

01:18:22.955 --> 01:18:24.835
Jennifer!
Get your stuff out here!

01:18:24.875 --> 01:18:26.795
10 minutes!

01:18:26.835 --> 01:18:28.755
