of recommendation.

01:19:00.155 --> 01:19:02.035
I felt very deeply
for Jennifer.

01:19:02.075 --> 01:19:02.995
Real affection.

01:19:03.035 --> 01:19:04.395
Touching.

01:19:04.435 --> 01:19:05.395
Even so, I made up
my mind to give her up

01:19:05.435 --> 01:19:06.835
