01:19:08.795 --> 01:19:10.155
But I can't.

01:19:10.195 --> 01:19:11.915
I care for her too much.

01:19:11.955 --> 01:19:13.595
Why the hell
wouldn't you?

01:19:13.635 --> 01:19:16.275
She's adorable, sweet,
smart, innocent.

01:19:16.315 --> 01:19:18.915
Mostly!
You'd have to be
even more senile

01:19:18.955 --> 01:19:20.835
than you are
not to care for her.

01:19:20.875 --> 01:19:22.515
I am not senile.

01:19:22.555 --> 01:19:24.155
I'm crazy about her.

01:19:24.195 --> 01:19:26.595
What the hell are you doing,
asking for her hand?

01:19:26.635 --> 01:19:28.995
With this teething ring,
I thee wed?

01:19:29.035 --> 01:19:29.915
Is that it?

01:19:29.955 --> 01:19:31.355
You want permission
to marry?

01:19:31.395 --> 01:19:33.635
Ask your wife first.
That's better manners.

01:19:33.675 --> 01:19:35.995
Hey, but wait a minute,
if she says no,

01:19:35.995 --> 01:19:38.355
maybe you and Karen
could adopt Jennifer.

01:19:38.395 --> 01:19:40.915
I could still see her.
I could baby-sit.

01:19:40.955 --> 01:19:43.155
She is a woman, Victor.
She's very mature.

01:19:43.195 --> 01:19:45.395
Too bad we can't say
the same thing about you!

01:19:45.395 --> 01:19:47.555
I love her.
It's as simple as that

01:19:47.595 --> 01:19:49.715
sure, you do!
What else can you say?

01:19:49.715 --> 01:19:50.635
I'm serious!

01:19:50.675 --> 01:19:52.555
I never thought I could
care this much again!

01:19:52.555 --> 01:19:54.955
