01:20:22.595 --> 01:20:25.075
Karen,
I've been unfaithful.

01:20:25.115 --> 01:20:26.475
Matthew!

01:20:26.515 --> 01:20:27.835
Is this a joke?

01:20:27.875 --> 01:20:29.795
