the punch line.

01:20:29.835 --> 01:20:31.635
Matthew?

01:20:31.675 --> 01:20:33.395
It's true.

01:20:33.435 --> 01:20:34.275
Ask him with who.

01:20:34.315 --> 01:20:35.115
Shut up, Victor!

01:20:35.155 --> 01:20:37.515
Karen, can we be alone?

01:20:37.555 --> 01:20:40.435
I think you have been
alone long enough.

01:20:40.475 --> 01:20:41.635
Who is she?

01:20:41.675 --> 01:20:43.195
Jennifer.

01:20:43.235 --> 01:20:44.955
Jennifer who?

01:20:44.995 --> 01:20:46.635
Jennifer?

01:20:46.675 --> 01:20:48.115
Cute little sweet
little Jennifer?

01:20:48.155 --> 01:20:49.595
Yeah.

01:20:49.635 --> 01:20:50.555
That little bitch.

01:20:50.595 --> 01:20:52.755
Wait a minute.
Jennifer's my daughter.

01:20:52.795 --> 01:20:54.915
Exactly! How could
you let this happen?

01:20:54.955 --> 01:20:56.355
Me? How could i
let it happen?

01:20:56.395 --> 01:20:57.555
He had no idea.

01:20:57.595 --> 01:20:58.715
Does Nicky know?

01:20:58.755 --> 01:21:01.115
Nicky who?
You bastard.

01:21:01.155 --> 01:21:04.035
I didn't mean
to be a bastard.

01:21:04.075 --> 01:21:06.915
Oh, I know.
It's just a gift.

01:21:07.075 --> 01:21:08.755
Is that
your composition, dear?

01:21:08.795 --> 01:21:10.435
"What I did on
my summer vacation."

01:21:10.475 --> 01:21:12.395
I came here
as fast as I could

01:21:12.435 --> 01:21:14.315
because I thought
you needed me.

01:21:14.355 --> 01:21:16.195
You didn't need me.
You were fine.

01:21:16.235 --> 01:21:18.155
A fantasy come true.

01:21:18.155 --> 01:21:19.995
