I was out every night.

01:21:25.835 --> 01:21:28.155
Oh, really?

01:21:28.195 --> 01:21:30.115
No big deal.
Just for dinner.

01:21:30.155 --> 01:21:31.035
I'm sure.

01:21:31.075 --> 01:21:32.995
Why do you have
to explain to her?

01:21:33.035 --> 01:21:34.395
I don't. Really.

01:21:34.435 --> 01:21:36.835
Exactly. What you do
is none of my business.

01:21:36.875 --> 01:21:38.315
What you do is.

01:21:38.355 --> 01:21:40.035
But it's important
that you understand-

01:21:40.075 --> 01:21:41.715
Victor, this is between
Matthew and me.

01:21:41.755 --> 01:21:43.155
I'm not just
an outsider here.

01:21:43.195 --> 01:21:44.075
