01:21:44.115 --> 01:21:46.035
Victor, you have
every right to be hurt.

01:21:46.075 --> 01:21:48.515
I know how much
you love her.

01:21:48.555 --> 01:21:49.475
Who said I love her?

01:21:49.515 --> 01:21:50.875
Victor!

01:21:50.915 --> 01:21:52.915
Are you saying
you don't love Jennifer?

01:21:52.915 --> 01:21:56.475
Of course I love her.
What do you take me for?

01:21:56.515 --> 01:22:01.275
Who did you think I meant?

01:22:01.315 --> 01:22:04.115
What's going on here?

01:22:04.155 --> 01:22:05.835
I've wanted to tell you,
Matthew.

01:22:05.875 --> 01:22:07.515
It's what I went away
to think about.

01:22:07.555 --> 01:22:08.435
Tell me what?

01:22:08.475 --> 01:22:10.355
We're in love.
No, we're not!

01:22:10.395 --> 01:22:11.835
What do you mean,
"we're in love"?

01:22:11.875 --> 01:22:13.235
What do you mean
we're not?

01:22:13.275 --> 01:22:15.195
Quiet, both of you!
I can't lead a double life.

01:22:15.235 --> 01:22:17.595
You had that kind
of marriage. I don't.

01:22:17.595 --> 01:22:19.035
Are you two
having an affair?

01:22:19.035 --> 01:22:19.955
Were.

