Victor and you?

01:22:25.755 --> 01:22:28.595
He's offended,
mr. Clean.

01:22:28.595 --> 01:22:30.635
No wonder you were so upset
she wasn't coming.

01:22:30.675 --> 01:22:32.035
More upset than you.

01:22:32.075 --> 01:22:35.435
So preoccupied all the time.
So injured. So self-righteous.

01:22:35.435 --> 01:22:37.835
Sleeping with someone else's
wife doesn't count?

01:22:37.835 --> 01:22:40.195
At least your wife isn't
anybody's daughter

01:22:40.235 --> 01:22:41.395
how could you?

01:22:41.435 --> 01:22:42.515
How could I?

01:22:42.555 --> 01:22:44.395
Mom?

01:22:44.435 --> 01:22:45.715
Nicky, darling.

01:22:45.755 --> 01:22:46.995
How could you?

01:22:47.035 --> 01:22:49.435
We were in love.
That makes a difference.

01:22:49.435 --> 01:22:51.995
Iove?

01:22:51.995 --> 01:22:52.955
We weren't
just looking for a thrill.

01:22:52.995 --> 01:22:54.715
Is that why you did it?

01:22:54.715 --> 01:22:56.875
Listen to this...

01:22:56.915 --> 01:22:59.315
"Matthew dearest, I don't
want to go on without you.

01:22:59.315 --> 01:23:03.595
"I'll dream of you
eternally."

01:23:15.715 --> 01:23:17.635
The last time we were
together like this,

01:23:17.635 --> 01:23:19.995
