for her to be born.

01:23:20.035 --> 01:23:22.395
Victor?

01:23:22.395 --> 01:23:25.275
As strange as it
may sound,

01:23:25.315 --> 01:23:28.435
I love you.

01:23:28.475 --> 01:23:31.515
Senhor Lyons?

01:23:31.555 --> 01:23:35.795
Yes?

01:23:35.835 --> 01:23:39.675
