01:24:09.835 --> 01:24:11.195
No.

01:24:11.235 --> 01:24:13.155
Is she allowed
visitors, doctor?

01:24:13.195 --> 01:24:16.915
One, perhaps, and...

01:24:16.955 --> 01:24:20.715
