my stomach

01:24:27.835 --> 01:24:29.795
mmm.

01:24:29.835 --> 01:24:32.235
I'm not on any kind
of machine, am I?

01:24:32.275 --> 01:24:33.155
Believe me, Jennifer,

01:24:33.195 --> 01:24:35.595
