first, you little shit.

01:24:48.275 --> 01:24:49.635
When you get older,

01:24:49.675 --> 01:24:52.075
and obviously you're going
to get a second chance at that,

01:24:52.115 --> 01:24:54.275
you'll find you can't have
whatever you want,

01:24:54.275 --> 01:24:57.515
and there's a price
for everything you get

01:24:57.555 --> 01:25:00.715
and sometimes other people
have to pay it.

01:25:00.755 --> 01:25:02.755
He loves you.

01:25:02.795 --> 01:25:04.715
He told me.

01:25:04.755 --> 01:25:07.635
That you talked together
bothers me more than anything.

01:25:07.635 --> 01:25:10.035
It's all my fault,
really.

01:25:10.035 --> 01:25:11.755
He never had a chance.

01:25:11.795 --> 01:25:14.235
Men seldom do.

01:25:14.275 --> 01:25:16.115
Please...

01:25:16.155 --> 01:25:18.995
don't hate me.

01:25:19.035 --> 01:25:23.355
It's more like envy.

01:25:28.515 --> 01:25:30.675
Karen?

01:25:30.715 --> 01:25:32.835
Go away.

01:25:35.715 --> 01:25:37.115
Nicky?

01:25:37.155 --> 01:25:42.035
