01:25:51.195 --> 01:25:52.115
Bastard.

01:25:52.155 --> 01:25:53.035
Prick.

01:25:53.075 --> 01:25:54.435
And to think
I said I love you.

01:25:54.435 --> 01:25:56.315
To who?
To you

01:25:56.355 --> 01:25:57.875
you love anything
that stands still.

01:25:57.915 --> 01:25:59.675
Unlike some
people I know.

01:25:59.715 --> 01:26:00.635
Screw you.

01:26:00.635 --> 01:26:02.835
Bloody hypocrite.

01:26:02.875 --> 01:26:04.915
I used to feel guilty
about me and Karen.

01:26:04.955 --> 01:26:06.995
Just don't think that
my being with Jennifer

01:26:07.035 --> 01:26:09.955
lets you off the hook.

01:26:09.995 --> 01:26:10.875
Move over.

01:26:10.915 --> 01:26:12.355
You don't deserve her,
you know that?

01:26:12.395 --> 01:26:13.555
Which one?

01:26:13.595 --> 01:26:14.675
Both. Either.

01:26:14.675 --> 01:26:15.675
Neither do you.

01:26:15.715 --> 01:26:17.635
Tough.
Karen's not going back.

01:26:17.675 --> 01:26:18.555
Like hell she isn't!

01:26:18.595 --> 01:26:20.755
I thought
you wanted Jennifer!

01:26:20.795 --> 01:26:22.875
Give me some!
Give me half!

01:26:22.915 --> 01:26:25.315
