Who are you, my goddamn wife?

01:26:25.315 --> 01:26:26.755
You want to be
Jennifer's mother, too?

01:26:26.755 --> 01:26:28.195
Stop throwing
Jennifer up to me!

01:26:28.195 --> 01:26:29.595
And you can
stop pretending

01:26:29.635 --> 01:26:31.515
you've got some kind
of moral superiority

01:26:31.555 --> 01:26:32.955
because you are a fraud!

01:26:32.955 --> 01:26:34.875
