hit me when you found out!

01:26:34.915 --> 01:26:36.315
Still want me
to hit you? Huh?

01:26:36.355 --> 01:26:38.235
Yeah? How about now?

01:26:38.275 --> 01:26:39.635
Fine!

01:26:39.675 --> 01:26:42.075
