from kicking!

01:26:50.275 --> 01:26:51.915
Aah!

01:26:51.955 --> 01:26:53.555
Let go!

01:26:53.595 --> 01:26:55.035
I'll kill you!

01:26:55.075 --> 01:26:56.715
Shut up!

01:26:56.755 --> 01:26:58.355
Aah!

01:26:58.395 --> 01:26:58.875
Watch it!
Those are my balls

01:26:58.915 --> 01:26:59.795
are you kidding?

01:26:59.835 --> 01:27:03.675
